  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=z14r54416e]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=z14r54416e]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473248980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=759\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473248980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1073\" data-width=\"1074\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619642916\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"12311083-b0ea-412a-820f-c05d2bd0c4a5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473248980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1074&amp;height=1073 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/CookiesNMilk_new_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473248980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=759 1x\" /></span><h2 id=\"BestPractices-MilkBottle-MilkBottle\">Milk Bottle</h2><p>Now we can take a look at the Milk and Bottle.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"milkNCookies_milkCloseTop.jpg\" width=\"396\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_milkCloseTop.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473593433&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=594\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/milkNCookies_milkCloseTop.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473593433&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"600\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619413597\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"milkNCookies_milkCloseTop.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"cbe9ffb6-10db-4969-9055-46bb77b78f9a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_milkCloseTop.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473593433&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=600 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_milkCloseTop.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473593433&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=594 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"milkNCookies_milk.jpg\" width=\"396\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_milk.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473596891&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=594\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/milkNCookies_milk.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473596891&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"600\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619446314\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"milkNCookies_milk.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"455cdd13-ba56-424f-b5f8-e5a1ec1bc379\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_milk.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473596891&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=600 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_milk.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473596891&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=594 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>The milk itself is un-textured and will be covered later, so we'll isolate the bottle and discuss how it achieves the &quot;dirty bottle&quot; look realistically.</p><p>Glass possesses several unique characteristics that make it special. And because of this, the PxrSurface material has an entire section designed to recreate glass and the most common looks. To understand imperfect and dirty glass, try to dissect what's happening in the image. For imperfect glass, there will be variations of roughness across the surface. Unlike crystal and a few other surfaces, many older and worn glass objects are not perfectly reflective or transmissive (refractive). There's also the addition of fingerprints and smudges on the surface of the glass. You can use masks to generate these and add them to the diffuse lobe to mix in additional elements, such as dirt, paint, and dust.</p><p>Layering this effect more easily has two options we'll talk about, and a third concern about trace depth covered in another document:</p><ul><li><p>Using <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-26.pixar.com/space/REN26/19661463\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrLayerSurface</u></a> to separate and then combine the shading of the glass and the dirt.</p></li><li><p>Correct UV layout to prevent texture repetition on the inside and outside.</p></li><li><p>Controlling <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-26.pixar.com/space/REN26/19661825\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>ray depth</u></a> appropriately to get the correct physical result for glass.</p></li></ul><p /><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"40d29113-c623-400b-b23f-2acf947046df\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>It's best to model objects volumetrically. They should have actual thickness, and the space between the glass surfaces works just the way it does in the real world, and should behave as you would expect. Avoid using two-dimensional models unless it makes sense to do so, such as for things like leaves or paper.</p></div></div><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"e5fa2627-b353-4dd1-a6ee-d9834ab8cca7\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>When rendering most glass containers with liquids, it's helpful to understand <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-26.pixar.com/space/REN26/19661549\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>intersection priority</u></a> to avoid artifacts and &quot;air gaps&quot;. This is technically known as the dielectric interface or nested dielectrics.</p></div></div><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"milkNCookies_emptyBottle.jpg\" width=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_emptyBottle.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473707377&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=600\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/milkNCookies_emptyBottle.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473707377&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"600\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619413607\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"milkNCookies_emptyBottle.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"97f543b3-3698-487b-82a6-f97ffa27f90c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_emptyBottle.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473707377&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=600 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_emptyBottle.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473707377&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=600 1x\" /></span><p /><p>First, we'll examine the glass layer by removing the upper layers of dirt and milk.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"milkNCookies_emptyBottleNoDirt.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_emptyBottleNoDirt.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473759138&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=534\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/milkNCookies_emptyBottleNoDirt.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473759138&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"600\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619479096\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"milkNCookies_emptyBottleNoDirt.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"c30b5642-1ab4-4675-ba04-a88bcaa9f788\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_emptyBottleNoDirt.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473759138&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=600 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_emptyBottleNoDirt.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473759138&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=534 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"milkNCookies_emptyBottleNoDirtFar.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_emptyBottleNoDirtFar.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473762994&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=534\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/milkNCookies_emptyBottleNoDirtFar.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473762994&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"600\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619511859\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"milkNCookies_emptyBottleNoDirtFar.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"e3008c87-f53e-4902-974d-7fc9b31efe62\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_emptyBottleNoDirtFar.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473762994&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=600 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_emptyBottleNoDirtFar.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759473762994&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=534 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>In the glass base material, the diffuse channel has some dirt at a low gain of 0.2. The low gain, combined with a darker texture, will ensure the effect isn't too opaque, which would make the bottle appear to be made of glass. </p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"DiffuseGlass.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/DiffuseGlass.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759474236747&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/DiffuseGlass.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759474236747&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619413614\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DiffuseGlass.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"e9ccd307-f780-4d4d-a75d-0c9fce38e5e7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/DiffuseGlass.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759474236747&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/DiffuseGlass.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759474236747&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>In the glass base material the diffuse channel has some dirt at a low gain of 0.2. The low gain combined with a darker texture will insure the effect isn't too opaque which would make the bottle look like it wasn't made of glass. </p><p>Notice the interior and exterior walls of the bottle are mapped separately. It doesn't usually make sense for a fingerprint to be on the outside&nbsp;<em>and</em>&nbsp;inside of a bottle.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"GlassSpecular.jpg\" width=\"396\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/GlassSpecular.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759474296836&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=396\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/GlassSpecular.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759474296836&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619511882\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"GlassSpecular.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"9c13f1b4-aed1-4a7d-8ab0-d10f7eeb961e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/GlassSpecular.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759474296836&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/GlassSpecular.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1759474296836&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=396&amp;height=396 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>The reflection gain is textured just like the tray and table to define where the bottle is most reflective or the least worn and dirty.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Glassrefraction.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/Glassrefraction.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474331340&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/Glassrefraction.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474331340&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619446348\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Glassrefraction.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"9510abc0-a875-45d7-900f-4aa46c7b9d11\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/Glassrefraction.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474331340&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/Glassrefraction.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474331340&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>The refraction color is what tints or attenuates the transmission of light through the glass. In this case, to imply more imperfections, a map has been connected to this color input. The white areas signal that the glass in these areas is clear <em>and</em> colorless.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RGlossinessGlass.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/RGlossinessGlass.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474549205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/RGlossinessGlass.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474549205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619479117\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RGlossinessGlass.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"ebff095c-b00b-42b7-a459-385faf49f80d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/RGlossinessGlass.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474549205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/RGlossinessGlass.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474549205&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>The roughness is similar to the diffuse map, but the color has been removed, and the black point has been altered. This means there should be no area on the texture that's perfectly black or has a value of 0, 0, 0. </p><p>Instead, it's slightly increased to 2% to add a subtle roughness to even the clearest areas, which is realistic for this image.</p><p /><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><p>Above this glass layer is a simple dried milk smudge map applied as an upper layer in the PxrLayerSurface. A simple mask is applied to a white diffuse color. </p><p>Below is the diffuse color and mask rendered on the bottle.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"milkNCookies_milkCoverBottleLarge.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_milkCoverBottleLarge.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474604801&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=534\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/milkNCookies_milkCoverBottleLarge.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474604801&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"600\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619413622\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"milkNCookies_milkCoverBottleLarge.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"43786238-9ea5-442c-b80c-8a169b69f409\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_milkCoverBottleLarge.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474604801&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=600 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_milkCoverBottleLarge.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474604801&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=534 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"milkNCookies_milkCoverBottle.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_milkCoverBottle.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474608266&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=534\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/milkNCookies_milkCoverBottle.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474608266&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"600\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619413628\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"milkNCookies_milkCoverBottle.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"87c0a91c-3216-4a1d-a67e-2bdfb34d3cf5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_milkCoverBottle.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474608266&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=600 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkNCookies_milkCoverBottle.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474608266&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=534 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"glassMilkMask.jpg\" width=\"356\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/glassMilkMask.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474651031&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/glassMilkMask.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474651031&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619413634\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"glassMilkMask.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"8e23a56c-5d14-43b6-a1d6-b6f34e16bad8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/glassMilkMask.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474651031&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/glassMilkMask.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474651031&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=356&amp;height=356 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Here is the mask used; it is applied in the PxrLayerMixer to globally control the &quot;MilkDirt_Layer&quot;</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><p>These are then combined for the final result. You'll find this to be straightforward with the Mix node that's auto-created when you select the option to make a PxrLayerSurface material.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"milkBottleNetwork.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkBottleNetwork.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474680177&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=607\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/milkBottleNetwork.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474680177&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"765\" data-width=\"957\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619413640\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"milkBottleNetwork.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"461ad3b7-7aad-4011-8dd4-fd3c29f812b9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkBottleNetwork.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474680177&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=957&amp;height=765 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/milkBottleNetwork.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759474680177&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=607 1x\" /></span><p /><p /><hr /><h3 id=\"BestPractices-MilkBottle-NextSteps\"><span data-colorid=\"z14r54416e\">Next Steps</span></h3><p>Cool, we&rsquo;ve dialed in the look for the glass milk bottle.  Let&rsquo;s now look at the milk itself.</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/608927745/Best+Practices+-+The+Tray\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608927745\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"previousLesson.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/previousLesson.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474804898&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=46\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/previousLesson.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474804898&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"67\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619642913\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"previousLesson.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"fe9d4e28-69b6-488b-81b6-fc5905134e91\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/previousLesson.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474804898&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=67 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/previousLesson.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474804898&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=46 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/619708417/Best+Practices+-+The+Milk\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619708417\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"nextLesson.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/nextLesson.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474804957&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=46\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/nextLesson.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474804957&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"67\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619642910\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"nextLesson.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"5b135ca5-a710-4582-b83b-bbb4a995c869\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/nextLesson.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474804957&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=67 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/nextLesson.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474804957&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=46 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" width=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474804989&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/619642881/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474804989&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"100\" data-width=\"100\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"619642907\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"619642881\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"dec0d58d-17f8-4295-9c27-95f4d1bd897d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474804989&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/619642881/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759474804989&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
